## Raw artefacts

- Raw Lighthouse JSON (10 reports): `/tmp/cwv-2026-04-24/{mobile,desktop}-{home,listing,pdp,cart,checkout}.json`
- Parser that produced the tables: `/tmp/cwv-2026-04-24/parse.js`
- Deep-dive opportunity + element scanner: `/tmp/cwv-2026-04-24/deep.js`, `deep2.js`, `deep4.js`

Rerun any single route with:

```
npx lighthouse https://janicka-shop.vercel.app/<path> \
  --only-categories=performance --quiet \
  --chrome-path=/usr/bin/chromium-browser \
  --chrome-flags="--headless=new --no-sandbox"
```

(add `--preset=desktop` for desktop profile; mobile is default.)
